## Project Rules
- All Win32 unsafe calls are isolated in `src/window.rs` — no unsafe in other modules
- Template matching lives exclusively in `src/vision.rs`
- Mouse/keyboard actions live exclusively in `src/actions.rs`
- MCP tool dispatch and server setup live exclusively in `src/main.rs`
- All numeric constants (confidence thresholds, timeouts, buffer sizes) live in `src/state/`
- Windows-platform dependencies are declared under `[target.'cfg(windows)'.dependencies]`
- enigo and rmcp are used only in `src/actions.rs` and `src/main.rs` respectively
- `SetForegroundWindow` must be called before every capture or click action

